title: NFL Week 7 point spreads, over/under: Giants a 3.5-point favorite over Cowboys
text:
Comments 
The New York Giants are a 3.5-point favorite over the Dallas Cowboys in an NFC East battle on Sunday. 
The Giants (3-3) are coming off a 20-point loss to the Philadelphia Eagles on Monday night. The Cowboys (2-3) have lost three games in a row without injured quarterback Tony Romo. 
The Buffalo Bills are a 4.5-point favorite for their game against the Jacksonville Jaguars on Sunday in London.
